experiment THEMIS
instrument TRO
start 2011 11 09 1800
end 2011 11 09 2400
status R
description Conjunction with THEMIS and Geotail - Substorm study
contact Frédéric Pitout
email frederic.pitout@irap.omp.eu
operator STAFF
submitter Frédéric Pitout
resources FR(6)
notes
We will make the most of ground-satellites conjunctions to study the nightside
ionospheric dynamics and magnetosphere-ionosphere coupling during substorms. We
shall be using all transmitting radars to have a full latitudinal coverage of
the ionospheric dynamics plus two altitude profiles of the ionospheric
parameters at ESR and UHF latitudes.
